<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Joel on Christian Internet Resources</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/joel/</link><description>Recent content in Joel on Christian Internet Resources</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/joel/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Joel 1</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/joel/chapter-01/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/joel/chapter-01/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="joel-chapter-1">Joel Chapter 1&lt;/h2>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpFirst" align=center style='margin-top:0in;margin-right: 0in;margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.25in;text-align:center;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>A Message from the L&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%; font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>ORD&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> to Joel Son of Pethuel&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="mourning-over-a-locust-invasion">Mourning over a Locust Invasion&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;a name="_Hlk122885644">&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;/a>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Listen to this, elders;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      pay attention, everybody in the land.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Has anything like this ever happened in your lifetime&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      or your ancestors’ lifetime?&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v3" id="v3">&lt;sup class="verse-num">3&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Tell your descendants about it;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Joel 2</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/joel/chapter-02/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/joel/chapter-02/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="joel-chapter-2">Joel Chapter 2&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="the-day-of-the-lord">The Day of the LORD&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;a name="_Hlk122886147">&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;/a>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Blow a bugle in Zion;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      sound an alarm on my holy mountain!&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      Let the people in the land tremble&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            because the day of the L&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%; font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>ORD&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> is coming.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      It’s near,&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;b>&lt;sup>&lt;span style='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  2&lt;/span>&lt;/sup>&lt;/b>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>a dark and gloomy day,&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Joel 3</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/joel/chapter-03/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/joel/chapter-03/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="joel-chapter-3">Joel Chapter 3&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="judgment-against-enemy-nations">Judgment Against Enemy Nations&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:.5in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.5in;'>&lt;a name="_Hlk122886663">&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;/a>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“When I restore the fortunes of Judah and Jerusalem, &lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>I’ll gather the nations to the Valley of Jehoshaphat and condemn them there on behalf of Israel, my permanent possession, my people. They scattered them among the nations, divided up my land, &lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="verse verse-v3" id="v3">&lt;sup class="verse-num">3&lt;/sup> &lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>cast lots for my people, traded a boy for a prostitute, and sold a girl for wine to get drunk on. &lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>